WEBVTT

00:01.172 --> 00:03.474
SO WHAT DID YOU DO
LAST NIGHT?

00:03.474 --> 00:07.007
OH, I TOOK ADVANTAGE
OF A LONELY, VULNERABLE WOMAN.

00:07.007 --> 00:09.080
OH, RIGHT, RIGHT, RIGHT.

00:09.080 --> 00:12.083
HEY, DID YOU LIKE IT WHEN
I KISSED THE BACK OF YOUR KNEE?

00:12.083 --> 00:16.187
