ABOUT THIS A LOT--
WERE YOU UP ALL NIGHT, TOO?

00:19.450 --> 00:21.452
OH, NO, I'M A GUY.

00:21.452 --> 00:25.096
BY "A LOT," I MEAN THE FIVE
MINUTES I'VE BEEN AWAKE.
MY BAD. GO ON.

00:25.096 --> 00:27.198
