00:27.198 --> 00:30.131
AND THIS--THIS LITTLE GROUP
OF OURS...

00:30.131 --> 00:33.364
THE CUL-DE-SAC CREW.
YEAH, I'M NOT GONNA CALL 'EM
THAT. UM, THIS LITTLE GROUP...

00:33.364 --> 00:37.168
THE CREW.
RIGHT. WELL, UM,
IT MEANS A LOT TO ME,

00:37.168 --> 00:39.640
AND OUR FRIENDSHIP
MEANS A LOT TO ME.

00:39.640 --> 00:42.042
I DON'T WANT TO
MESS THAT UP.

00:42.042 --> 00:43.814
I DON'T EITHER.

00:43.814 --> 00:47.278
MAYBE THIS SHOULD JUST BE
A-A ONETIME DEAL.

00:47.278 --> 00:51.051
OR... WE COULD
JUST BE FRIENDS...

00:51.051 --> 00:53.053
(under breath) WITH BENEFITS.

00:53.053 --> 00:57.088
OH, YOU SNUCK THAT IN
AT THE END, DIDN'T YA?

00:57.088 --> 00:59.090
