THE OLD F.W.B.

00:59.090 --> 01:01.392
THAT IS THE GREATEST MALE MYTH
OF OUR TIME.

01:01.392 --> 01:04.365
I MEAN, THAT AND OUR KNEES
BEING AN EROGENOUS ZONE.

01:04.365 --> 01:06.367
IT IS.
IT'S NOT. IT'S A KNEE.

01:06.367 --> 01:09.770
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHY F.W.B. NEVER WORKS?

01:09.770 --> 01:13.804
NO.
WE'RE FRIENDS.
IT CAN'T BE CASUAL.

01:13.804 --> 01:16.607
