WITH FEELINGS AND BAGGAGE,

01:16.607 --> 01:19.480
AND SOMEONE ALWAYS GETS HURT.
IT'S A HORRIBLE IDEA.

01:19.480 --> 01:23.284
(Laurie)
JULES, IT'S COFFEE TIME!
STAY HERE.
I DON'T WANT THEM TO KNOW.

01:23.284 --> 01:26.117
(lowered voice)
BUT I LOVE COFFEE TIME.

01:26.117 --> 01:28.619
