WHAT MAGAZINE?

01:59.220 --> 02:02.223
FINE! IT'S JUST--I FEEL LIKE
PEOPLE RESPECT MY IDEAS MORE

02:02.223 --> 02:04.825
WHEN THEY THINK THAT
THEY CAME OUT OF MAGAZINES.
NOPE.

02:04.825 --> 02:07.758
I'LL GO FIRST
BECAUSE I GOT NOTHING TO HIDE.

02:07.758 --> 02:10.161
