BUT THEN THEY WENT RIGHT BACK.

02:13.164 --> 02:14.905
WHATEVS.

02:14.905 --> 02:17.908
ONCE, WHILE YOU WERE ASLEEP,
I KISSED YOU ON THE FOREHEAD

02:17.908 --> 02:21.242
'CAUSE I WANTED YOU
TO HAVE NICE DREAMS.
NO, I KNOW. I WAS AWAKE.

02:21.242 --> 02:23.914
