SO THEY KNOW HOW ANNOYING IT IS.

02:39.260 --> 02:41.532
(chuckles) GOOD LUCK, SISTERS.
NOT THAT EASY.

02:41.532 --> 02:43.534
IT'S NEVER HARD FOR ME.

02:43.534 --> 02:47.198
THAT'S WHAT HE SAID. WHOO!
OH! (speaks gibberish)

02:47.198 --> 02:49.700
(speaks gibberish)
HA!

02:49.700 --> 02:51.372
