THIS PLACE IS RELEASING

03:16.427 --> 03:18.429
A BALLOON
WITH 2,000 BUCKS IN IT.

03:18.429 --> 03:20.431
DAD, YOU CAN'T PUT
ALL YOUR FINANCIAL HOPES

03:20.431 --> 03:21.932
INTO BALLOON CHASING.

03:21.932 --> 03:24.935
