IT WOULD BE NICE FOR YOU

03:48.359 --> 03:51.502
TO HAVE SOME HELP AROUND
THE HOUSE AND NOT BE TIED DOWN.

03:51.502 --> 03:54.265
AND SO WHAT DO YOU THINK?
ELLIE.

03:56.407 --> 04:00.411
