WELL, SHE DOESN'T HAVE ONE.

05:19.420 --> 05:22.693
IT'S MY SPIRIT GUIDE.

05:22.693 --> 05:25.426
HEY, JULES. YOU LEFT
YOUR SUNGLASSES AT THE BAR.

05:25.426 --> 05:26.897
