09:14.184 --> 09:17.127
(whispers) HERE.
CAN YOU HOLD THIS FOR A SECOND?
(mouths word)

09:17.127 --> 09:19.129
OH! THERE IT IS.
BE COOL, MAN.

09:19.129 --> 09:22.132
